# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# .gitignore â€” FULLY COMMENTED HANDOVER
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# High-level context:
# This file prevents build outputs, local settings, and secrets from being tracked.
# It keeps the repo clean, reduces noise in diffs, and protects sensitive material.
#
# Organization:
# - Android/Gradle: build/, .gradle/, local.properties, .idea noise
# - NDK/CMake:      cmake-build-*/, obj/, intermediates/
# - Python:         __pycache__, .venv/, .mypy_cache/
# - Models:         large generated models if not versioned; prefer artifacts instead
# - OS files:       .DS_Store, Thumbs.db, etc.
#
# How to modify:
# - Add ignores for new toolchains or outputs (e.g., new /artifacts dir for CI).
# - Never ignore source files or critical config; be deliberate.
#
# Troubleshooting:
# - If a file is already tracked, updating .gitignore won't remove it. Use:
#       git rm --cached path/to/file
#   to untrack it while keeping it locally.
# ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
# --- Android / Gradle (generic)
# Ignore Gradle state/cache directories.
.gradle/
**/build/
**/.cxx/
**/.idea/
# IDE project files; reproducible devs shouldn't rely on these.
**/*.iml
# Local SDK path/keystore location; never commit.
local.properties

# --- Android / Gradle (your tree under python/mobile/android)
# Ignore Gradle state/cache directories.
python/mobile/android/.gradle/
python/mobile/android/**/build/
python/mobile/android/**/.cxx/
python/mobile/android/**/.idea/
# IDE project files; reproducible devs shouldn't rely on these.
python/mobile/android/**/*.iml
python/mobile/android/java_pid*.hprof
python/mobile/android/**/captures/
python/mobile/android/**/outputs/**/*.apk
python/mobile/android/**/outputs/**/*.aab

# --- OpenCV Android SDK (keep local; CI will fetch it)
python/mobile/android/app/src/main/cpp/third_party/OpenCV-android-sdk/
python/mobile/android/app/src/main/cpp/third_party/opencv*.zip

# --- Native/NDK compiled libs (covered by build/, but explicit for safety)
**/jniLibs/*.so

